<A>__{all ahead full! on the catwalk thomas andrews, the shipbuilder, watches carefully as the engineers and greasers scramble to adjust valves. towering above them are the twin reciprocating engines, four stories tall, their ten foot long connecting rods surging up and down with the turning of the massive crankshafts. the engines thunder like the footfalls of marching giants.}
